dict.string: This is just a sample. Do NOT try loading it.
Ensure you understand EVERY field before booting.
In most cases recommended to use Sample.plist
Use SampleCustom.plist only for special cases.
Comment: Fix AsRock Z390 BIOS DSDT Device(RTC) bug
change USTP, 8 to XSTP, 8 to, pair with SSDT-I2C1
Haswell: SB_RCBA is a 0x4 page memory region, containing SPI_BASE at 0x3800 (SPI_BASE_ADDRESS)
Generic: PCI root is a 0x1000 page memory region used by some firmwares
Change 15 Port Limit To 30 in XHCI Kext (X99-series)
change 15 port limit to 20 in XHCI kext (9-series)
Change 15 Port Limit To 30 in XHCI Kext 10.12(99-series)
Disable minStolenSize less or equal fStolenMemorySize assertion
disable port limit in XHCI kext (credit PMHeart)
disable port limit in XHCI kext (credit PMHeart)
Set the maximum link rate in DPCD buffer to 0x0A (HBR) for laptops with 1080p or below display
Set the number of active lanes to 2 (for laptop with 1080p or below display) (by FireWolf)
IONVMeFamily change 0x10 -> 0x01 for LiteOn CX2 (c) Pike R. Alpha implemented by Ricky for 10.14.4
IONVMeFamily: Ignore FLBAS bit:4 being set - for Plextor/LiteOn/Hynix
